    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as-is. While it remains a reliable runner, the exterior shows clear signs of age, including significant paint oxidation on the roof and hood, along with several noticeable scuffs on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and a small tear on the driver's side bolster. Mechanically, it starts and drives well, though it will likely need a suspension refresh and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s an ideal choice for a buyer looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point or someone looking for a project to restore.",
