    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom-quality condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, always garage-kept and pampered. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that 'new car' magic. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
