    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp with razor-sharp throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, the drivetrain is mechanically flawless. The chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including documented rear subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS overhaul. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers, ensuring telepathic handling. The exterior finish is concours-ready, while the interior retains its factory-fresh tactile feel. A turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
